preownedConditionTypes.conditionTypeDefinition: Item is in excellent condition, perfect working condition and has no signs of wear/usage. The original protective wrapping, if any, may be missing but the original packaging is intact.

Item is in excellent condition and has no signs of usage. The item is still in its original packaging, but packaging is open/has signs of wear. The item includes original accessories. This could include warehouse items, returns, etc.
Item shows wear from consistent use, but it remains in fair condition. The item may be marked, identified, or show other signs of previous use. The item remains usable.
A well-cared-for item that has seen limited use but remains in great condition. Item and instructions are complete and included.
A brand-new, unused functional item that has cosmetic imperfections caused during production or delivery. (Missing threads, discoloration, label malfunction, etc.)
A brand-new, unused item without original packaging.
A brand-new, unused item without original tags.
An original name brand cartridge that has been professionally cleaned, refilled with similar quality ink, and then tested to make sure you get the same print quality as the original cartridge.

_rawConfigs.preownedConditionSubHeadingName: What is the Walmart Pre-Owned Program?
_rawConfigs.preownedConditionSubHeadingContent: Walmart Pre-Owned allows you to find previously owned, well-cared-for items from Walmart’s trusted & performance-managed sellers. Shopping Pre-Owned allows you to bring home the best-quality picks at even lower prices, in addition to extending the life of an item & reducing waste. Find your favorites & shop a range of conditions in every category.

preownedConditionHighlights.highlightContent: Each Pre-Owned item listed comes from Walmart’s trusted performance-managed sellers, to ensure you get quality items.
Save even more on top brands & your most-loved items.
Don’t love it? Most items offer a 30-day* free return policy, for added peace of mind.
Shopping Pre-Owned helps in extending the life of an item & reducing waste.

customerReviews.reviewText: Love to shop them Men’s Dept. What a bargain!! $12.00 flannel top. I reviewed it on my Insta page and they loved it. @karenthefashionfinder
I've bought several of these George flannels and they have all been nice.  material is soft and the fit is perfect. Never had an issue .
Excellent price, quality, style and fit.  Ordered a second one in a different color.
Saw this shirt in store but they did not have my size. Ordered it and got it just a few days later! So soft and comfy!

My husband normally wears a medium in t-shirts and based on other reviews about this shirt running small or shrinking when laundered I purchased size large for him and they fit perfect. They definitely do shrink about 1 size even when laundered on delicate and dried on low heat. Other than the shrinking these are great quality flannel shirts at a great price!

Every year as a family, we take family pictures.
The men all dress up in matching flannel shirts. 
The women match up in similar colors.  
These shirts from Walmart were absolutely PERFECT,
at a very reasonable price.
Our family photos look great.

Literally have this flannel in every color it’s been made in since 2021. Every fall I all but run to the men’s section to get more! So soft, warm but lightweight, great for layering or tying around your waist with leggings. I’m female, 5’2”, 110 lbs, and the small fits me great and just a tiny bit oversized on me since it’s made for a broader male body type. I know this is supposed to be for the guys, but ladies… GO GET EVERY COLOR!! You won’t regret it.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: The best flannel I’ve ever owned. Yes, really.

customerReviews.reviewText: This is such a nice shirt. The Walmart picture doesn’t show how Smokey blue/grey this shirt is. It’s nicer in person. AND ITS ON A TALL!! Thank you for being inclusive to our tall guys!

Love the shirt! But I don't like the delivery driver driving into my yard to throw the package out of the car window! Images are from nest camera and nest doorbell camera. 1st image shows package in flight 2nd image shows Walmart package on the ground if you enlarge image you can see it is the same vehicle. I do have actual video.
